  "text": "Wondering if the one, Abraham Lincoln, could have possibly been a Wanderer? I am Ra. This is incorrect. This entity was a normal, shall we say, Earth being which chose to leave the vehicle and allow an entity to use it on a permanent basis. This is relatively rare compared to the phenomenon of Wanderers. You would do better considering the incarnations of Wanderers such as the one known as \"Thomas, \" the one known as \"Benjamin. \"",
